    <!-- Add Activity -->

    <activity>
        <statement>
            <p>
                <term>In groups:</term>
            </p>
            <p>
                <ol marker="(a)">
                    <li>
                        <p>Measure the length of the desk using a <m>15</m> cm ruler.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>Measure the same desk using a <m>30</m> cm ruler.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>Measure it using a metre rule or tape measure.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>Record all your results clearly.</p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </p>
            <tabular left="medium" right="medium" top="medium" bottom="medium">
                <row header="yes">
                    <cell>Measuring Tool</cell>
                    <cell>Length (cm)</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell><m>15</m> cm</cell>
                    <cell>?</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell><m>30</m> cm</cell>
                    <cell>?</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>Metre Rule</cell>
                    <cell>?</cell>
                </row>
            </tabular>
            <p>
                <term>Part B: Comparing Results</term>
            </p>
            <p>
                <ol marker="(i)">
                    <li>
                        <p>Do all groups obtain the same measurement? Explain.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>Which measuring tool gave the most consistent result? Why?</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>Which tool do you think is most accurate? Give reasons.</p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </p>
            <p>
                <term>Part C: Investigating Differences</term>
            </p>
            <p>
                <ol marker="(i)">
                    <li>
                        <p>Compare your results with another group's measurements.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>Suggest possible reasons why the results are different.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>Discuss how human error may have affected the results.</p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </p>
            <p>
                <term>Guided Reflection:</term>
            </p>
            <p>
                <ol marker="(a)">
                    <li>
                        <p>What happens if the ruler is not placed exactly at the edge of the desk?</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>Does the thickness of the measuring tool affect accuracy?</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>Can two correct measurements still be slightly different? Explain.</p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </p>
            <p>
                What are the ways of improving accuracy when measuring long objects.
            </p>
        </statement>
    </activity>

